# creating accounts

- Create twitter account
  - on the first screen, under "advanced", disable search by phone/email.
  - enter phone number
  - in the extension background console:

Twitter.createApp("Morecowbellsplz!").then(appInfo => Twitter.createAccessToken(appInfo.appId)).then(res => console.log(res))

- Create github account. skip as many steps as possible.
  (got flagged immediately after uploading a picture of rowan atkinson as the profile picture)


# Avoid prompts on first run

google-chrome-stable --user-data-dir=temp --make-default-browser --make-chrome-default

# chrome will create the user's profile folder and terminate right away.

# run it again without flags

google-chrome-stable --user-data-dir=temp
